  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      An observational study in patients with advanced ER+, HER2 negative breast cancer, who are
      treated with everolimus and exemestane in combination. The objective of the study is to
      assess the safety pattern of everolimus in a real world setting.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
